locations.adventureSummary:
At the Abandoned Camp, the party found evidence of a hasty bandit evacuation with empty cages and scattered belongings. Kira detected faint drag marks suggesting a captive was dragged away recently, prompting the party to follow the trail deeper into the woods with cautious resolve.

{
  "narration": "In the shadowed clearing of the abandoned camp, Eirik Hearthwise and Scout Kira faced a harrowing battle against two spectral Whispering Ashlings and a desperate Ashbound Bandit. The bandit launched frantic and wild attacks, initially catching Eirik off guard and cutting him, but was steadily worn down by Eirik's steadfast mace strikes and Kira's precise archery. Kira, though gravely wounded by the Ashlings' necrotic assaults, held her ground, delivering fatal shots that dissolved one Ashling and ultimately felled the bandit. Eirik's timely healing spells and radiant Sacred Flame worked to counter the spirits' chilling attacks. The last Ashling, nearly destroyed by Kira's final arrow after Eirik's sacred fire, dissipated in a wisp of shadow and whispered regret. With the bandit dead and both spirits vanquished, the clearing grew still, the oppressive cold lifting as victory was claimed. The encounter awarded 400 XP total, divided between the two participants, granting each 200 experience points. The battlefield was left strewn with the corpses of the fallen: the Ashbound Bandit lay lifeless, and the two Whispering Ashlings were no more than fading echoes as their spirits were banished.",
  "combat_round": 5,
  "actions": [
    "Round 1: Ashbound Bandit attacked Eirik but missed; Eirik struck back, damaging the bandit; Whispering Ashling_2 attempted Ashen Touch on Eirik but failed; Kira shot an arrow hitting Whispering Ashling_2.",
    "Round 2: Ashbound Bandit struck Eirik causing injury; Eirik healed with Cure Wounds; Kira shot and killed Whispering Ashling_2; Whispering Ashling struck Kira causing necrotic damage.",
    "Round 3: Eirik cast Healing Word to restore some health; attempted mace attack on bandit but missed; Kira wounded Whispering Ashling; the bandit remained standing wounded; Kira suffered from Ashling's attack.",
    "Round 4: Ashbound Bandit struck Eirik causing damage; Eirik wounded bandit critically; Kira prepared to shoot; Eirik delivered a crushing mace blow reducing bandit's HP drastically; Kira prepared her last arrow.",
    "Round 5: Bandit was finished by Kira's arrow upon Eirik's command; last Whispering Ashling attacked Kira but missed; Eirik cast Sacred Flame dealing radiant damage, banishing the last Ashling; Kira survived barely.",
    "No allies or enemies other than those described participated; bandit and both Ashlings died, leaving corpses and fading spirits in the clearing."
  ]
}

